LAGOS  – BetKing, the digital entertainment company, has delighted two of its customers with brand new Sports Utility Vehicles (SUVs) as part of its just-concluded AFKON campaign. The campaign, tagged: ‘#ThatAFKONFeeling’ was launched in January as part of the company’s efforts to celebrate African football and reward BetKing customers during this year’s edition of the African Cup of Nations (AFCON). A statement by the company stated that the car presentation ceremony, which took place at Ikoyi, Lagos February 13, 2022 had key stakeholders in attendance including Nigerian football legend and BetKing Brand Ambassador, Austin J.J. Okocha, BetKing and KingMakers executives, and media. Digital Online Marketing As A Tool Of Managing Your Brand (2) Digital Online Marketing As A Tool Of Managing Your Brand (1) The cars were presented to the winners – Joseph Ezugwu from Anambra State and Ugochukwu Nwagbo from Edo State by Okocha and Oladipo Olasope, Chief Financial Officer, Kingmakers. Oludare Kafar, Head, BTL Marketing, Kingmakers, while speaking at the event, said: “It’s been an exciting past few weeks and we are glad to wrap up the AFKON campaign in grand style as we reward two of some of our winners with brand new car prizes. “At BetKing, we are deeply committed to celebrating African football and rewarding our customers, hence, we look forward to future initiatives such as this. “As you can see, for this campaign, there is still one more brand new SUV available to be won, and we are on the search for the winner. We urge our customers to partake in this very exciting promo to stand a chance to win the third JAC SUV.” In addition to the cars, the three winners, the company said would also be receiving exclusive BetKing jackets officially signed by J.J. Okocha. One of the winners of the cars, Joseph Ezugwu, said, “I am beyond excited and very grateful to BetKing for my brand new SUV. Today, I truly feel like a king and I owe that to BetKing.”